		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />We previously speculated on the game in the photo in <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?t=4153" class="postlink">this topic</a>. One of the techniques for identifying which system (let alone game) involved counting metatiles: NES and Super NES games will have 8 or 16 metatiles across, not 20 as seen in this screenshot.

		

